View.CheckCode:
Page [Page A] Before
HIDE CollectionDate CollectionTime Collection_Type Placeholder SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed ContainerState Hide VisibleLarvaeQuantity InterventionType ContainerAccessibility SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence VisiblePupaeQuantity SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed OtherReasonForNotApplyingLarvicides
IF CollectionType = (.) THEN ASSIGN CollectionType = 0 ASSIGN CollectionDate = SYSTEMDATE ASSIGN CollectionTime = SYSTEMTIME END-IF IF LarvicidesUsed = 3 THEN UnHide SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed else Hide SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed
END-IF End-Before
After
IF CollectionType = 1 THEN GOTO IsContainerPositive END-IF End-After End-Page
Field CollectionType
Click IF CollectionType = 0 THEN ASSIGN Collection_Type = "Adulte"
ELSE
ASSIGN Collection_Type = "Larves/Pupes"
DIALOG "Dans votre sondage larves/pupes,Veuillez enregistrer tous les conteneurs qui ont de l'eau, même s'ils sont couverts. Excluez tous les conteneurs qui n'ont pas d'eau à l'intérieur." TITLETEXT="Rappel"
END-IF
End-Click End-Field
Page [Page B] After //add code here GOTO Placeholder End-After End-Page
Page [Page F] After IF ContainerTypes = "12" THEN GOTO CategoryBOtherContainer ELSE GOTO ContainerLocation END-IF End-After End-Page
Page InsertPage1 After //add code here GOTO ContainerTypes
End-After End-Page
Field IsContainerPositive Click IF IsContainerPositive= 1 THEN assign ContainerState = "Positif" Hide ContainerAccessibility SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence UnHide VisibleLarvaeQuantity VisiblePupaeQuantity InterventionType END-IF IF IsContainerPositive= 2 THEN assign ContainerState = "Négatif" Hide VisibleLarvaeQuantity InterventionType ContainerAccessibility SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence VisiblePupaeQuantity
END-IF IF IsContainerPositive= 3 THEN assign ContainerState = "Inconnu" Hide VisibleLarvaeQuantity VisiblePupaeQuantity SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence UNHide InterventionType ContainerAccessibility END-IF End-Click End-Field
Field LarvicidesUsed Click // SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed IF LarvicidesUsed = 3 THEN UnHide SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed else Hide SpecifyOtherLarvicidesUsed
END-IF
End-Click End-Field
Field ContainerAccessibility After
IF ContainerAccessibility = 1 OR ContainerAccessibility =(.) THEN Hide SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence else UnHide SpecifyUnknownLarvaePresence
END-IF
End-After End-Field
Field ReasonForNotApplyingLarvicide Click IF ReasonForNotApplyingLarvicide = 2 THEN UnHide OtherReasonForNotApplyingLarvicides else Hide OtherReasonForNotApplyingLarvicides
END-IF
End-Click End-Field
Page [Page C] After IF IsContainerPositive= 2 THEN GOTO NegativeTires ELSE IF InterventionType= 1 THEN GOTO ReasonForNotApplyingLarvicide END-IF IF InterventionType= 2 THEN GOTO ContainerTypes END-IF IF InterventionType = 3 THEN GOTO LarvicidesUsed END-IF END-IF // GOTO ContainerTypes End-After End-Page
Page InsertPage3 After
IF IsContainerPositive = 2 THEN GOTO Remarks Else GOTO ContainerLocation END-IF
End-After End-Page
Field AnyMosquitoesCaught After IF AnyMosquitoesCaught= (+) THEN assign ContainerState = "Positif"
Else assign ContainerState = "Négatif" END-IF
End-After End-Field
